                    <div class="flex items-center mb-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-paper-plane text-white text-2xl mr-2"></i>
                        <span class="font-bold text-xl text-white">SecureMail<span class="text-primary">Sender</span></span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="mb-4">Advanced email delivery platform with industry-leading deliverability and powerful features.</p>
                    <div class="flex space-x-4">
                        <a href="#" class="text-gray-400 hover:text-white"><i class="fab fa-twitter"></i></a>
