            <div class="border-t border-gray-800 mt-10 pt-6 text-center">
                <p class="text-sm">© 2023 SecureMailSender. All rights reserved. This platform should only be used for legitimate email marketing purposes in compliance with all applicable laws including CAN-SPAM and GDPR. We strictly prohibit the sending of unsolicited bulk emails or messages.</p>
